ize=1> I know how you feel, E. Two years ago I upgraded and in order to play Luclin I had to upgrade again. So I get everything new short of the video card which was once compatable with EQ. Now it's not, but oh, they don't announce this until AFTER the release and I've spent my money. Apparantly SB Live isn't either since I think that is what's causing the lockups. Though it is listed as being compatable, it seems not to be.<br>
